abstracts.cdata!:
The project consists of: (1)
            construction and installation of about 132.5 miles of 275 kV
            lines and associated substations to link up the Temengor
            Hydroelectric Scheme with NEB's system at Papan and to
            extend the main system southward from Port Dickson to
            Malacca; (2) extension of associated transmission and
            distribution system under 275 kV; (3) establishment of
            control and load dispatching center; and (4) provision of
            consulting services.
